    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's an interesting way to frame it. so if we use that hard power/realist logic, does that basically mean we should stop judging interventions based on whether they create democracy and just focus on whether they stop immediate violence or protect interests? like, is the \"liberal\" focus on stability actually just a distraction from what really matters in geopolitics?",
